00:20:56.680 --> 00:21:00.160 align:middle line:84%
And I said I'm not
taking them down.

00:21:00.160 --> 00:21:02.740 align:middle line:84%
And at that point, in that
struggle on the phone,

00:21:02.740 --> 00:21:08.350 align:middle line:90%
I knew this is not a CGI ploy.

00:21:08.350 --> 00:21:11.470 align:middle line:90%
This is not a Photoshop ploy.

00:21:11.470 --> 00:21:16.570 align:middle line:84%
In June, after I had
gotten those photos,

00:21:16.570 --> 00:21:20.820 align:middle line:84%
there was an email from a
man who called himself Isaac.

00:21:20.820 --> 00:21:23.830 align:middle line:84%
And here unfolds, I
think, personally,

00:21:23.830 --> 00:21:26.050 align:middle line:84%
one of the most
important whistleblower

00:21:26.050 --> 00:21:28.330 align:middle line:90%
leaks of my career.

00:21:28.330 --> 00:21:31.660 align:middle line:10%
This extremely important
whistleblower leak

00:21:31.660 --> 00:21:35.290 align:middle line:10%
contained a document that
had photos and texts in it

00:21:35.290 --> 00:21:40.060 align:middle line:10%
about an extraterrestrial
technology, named as such.

00:21:40.060 --> 00:21:41.980 align:middle line:10%
It was supposed to
have been developed

00:21:41.980 --> 00:21:46.040 align:middle line:10%
in something called the
Palo Alto Laboratory in Palo

00:21:46.040 --> 00:21:47.960 align:middle line:10%
Alto, California.

00:21:47.960 --> 00:21:52.180 align:middle line:84%
He had worked personally
in this lab in the '80s.

00:21:52.180 --> 00:21:56.260 align:middle line:84%
And the program was
called CARET, all caps--

00:21:56.260 --> 00:22:01.810 align:middle line:84%
Commercial Application Research
of Extraterrestrial Technology.

00:22:01.810 --> 00:22:04.840 align:middle line:84%
And these scientists
were working underground

00:22:04.840 --> 00:22:08.260 align:middle line:84%
in a building that, as
I understood from Isaac,

00:22:08.260 --> 00:22:12.100 align:middle line:84%
would have looked like a
two-story library in Palo Alto

00:22:12.100 --> 00:22:14.980 align:middle line:90%
on a leafy street with trees.

00:22:14.980 --> 00:22:19.420 align:middle line:84%
And the truth was, just like so
many government programs that

00:22:19.420 --> 00:22:22.450 align:middle line:84%
hide in plain sight,
If you had access

00:22:22.450 --> 00:22:25.150 align:middle line:84%
to get into the
library-looking building,

00:22:25.150 --> 00:22:30.160 align:middle line:84%
it went down floors and floors
and spread out underground.

00:22:30.160 --> 00:22:34.950 align:middle line:10%
And there were at least 200 or
300 scientists working there

00:22:34.950 --> 00:22:37.420 align:middle line:10%
for the Department
of Defense that

00:22:37.420 --> 00:22:40.450 align:middle line:10%
wanted to see if,
in the Palo Alto

00:22:40.450 --> 00:22:44.680 align:middle line:10%
atmosphere of the development
of computers like Apple

00:22:44.680 --> 00:22:49.750 align:middle line:10%
and so forth, that they could
accelerate scientists trying

00:22:49.750 --> 00:22:53.860 align:middle line:10%
to figure out what
they called a language

00:22:53.860 --> 00:22:56.650 align:middle line:10%
of these dragonfly drones.

00:22:56.650 --> 00:23:01.430 align:middle line:10%
Or, as Isaac said in
his communication,

00:23:01.430 --> 00:23:04.000 align:middle line:10%
I am convinced that the
photographs that you

00:23:04.000 --> 00:23:08.090 align:middle line:10%
are showing at earthfiles.com
is the same technology,

00:23:08.090 --> 00:23:10.810 align:middle line:10%
now large and in
the air, that we

00:23:10.810 --> 00:23:14.230 align:middle line:10%
were studying and back
engineering at this Palo Alto

00:23:14.230 --> 00:23:16.970 align:middle line:10%
lab in the '80s.

00:23:16.970 --> 00:23:20.450 align:middle line:10%
And I got to email
exchange with him

00:23:20.450 --> 00:23:23.900 align:middle line:10%
a very long dialogue after
looking at the document.

00:23:23.900 --> 00:23:28.160 align:middle line:84%
And I learned he had
become so frustrated,

00:23:28.160 --> 00:23:30.440 align:middle line:84%
the fact that it was a
Department of Defense

00:23:30.440 --> 00:23:31.460 align:middle line:90%
operation.

00:23:31.460 --> 00:23:33.280 align:middle line:90%
They had guns on them.

00:23:33.280 --> 00:23:35.420 align:middle line:84%
The scientists were
basically treated

00:23:35.420 --> 00:23:37.610 align:middle line:84%
like you do your
work in that corner

00:23:37.610 --> 00:23:39.470 align:middle line:84%
and you can't go over
here and everything

00:23:39.470 --> 00:23:41.270 align:middle line:90%
was compartmentalized.

00:23:41.270 --> 00:23:45.200 align:middle line:84%
His job was to study
symbols that they called

00:23:45.200 --> 00:23:48.110 align:middle line:90%
self-activating software.

00:23:48.110 --> 00:23:51.710 align:middle line:84%
Imagine if you had an
8.5 by 11 sheet of paper.

00:23:51.710 --> 00:23:56.660 align:middle line:84%
And it has been made with
a self-activating software.

00:23:56.660 --> 00:24:00.980 align:middle line:84%
All you would have to do
is look at the paper, think

00:24:00.980 --> 00:24:05.960 align:middle line:84%
what you wanted, who you wanted
it to go to, what building,

00:24:05.960 --> 00:24:06.890 align:middle line:90%
what country--

00:24:06.890 --> 00:24:08.750 align:middle line:90%
it would not matter.

00:24:08.750 --> 00:24:11.450 align:middle line:10%
You think it, the
paper from thereon--

00:24:11.450 --> 00:24:15.590 align:middle line:10%
because it's self-activating
software designed never to have

00:24:15.590 --> 00:24:18.590 align:middle line:10%
to need any person
or interface--

00:24:18.590 --> 00:24:19.790 align:middle line:10%
will take off.

00:24:19.790 --> 00:24:22.880 align:middle line:84%
It will accomplish everything
that you have thought.

00:24:22.880 --> 00:24:25.730 align:middle line:84%
And it will come back to
you when it has finished.

00:24:25.730 --> 00:24:29.030 align:middle line:84%
That is self-activating
software.

00:24:29.030 --> 00:24:34.040 align:middle line:10%
And Isaac explained, when
he sent these drawings

00:24:34.040 --> 00:24:38.120 align:middle line:10%
and he sent the ones that
were in the document, a team

00:24:38.120 --> 00:24:41.300 align:middle line:10%
of these engineers
and people like Isaac,

00:24:41.300 --> 00:24:43.340 align:middle line:10%
who was a computer expert.

00:24:43.340 --> 00:24:50.840 align:middle line:10%
They tried for 30 days to try
to duplicate with CRAYs what

00:24:50.840 --> 00:24:54.980 align:middle line:10%
they had as extraterrestrial
self-activating software.

00:24:54.980 --> 00:24:56.460 align:middle line:90%
And they still couldn't do it.

00:24:56.460 --> 00:24:58.850 align:middle line:90%
They could not duplicate.

00:24:58.850 --> 00:25:01.880 align:middle line:90%
It was infinitely complex.

00:25:01.880 --> 00:25:05.360 align:middle line:84%
And he said, in one
of his communications,

00:25:05.360 --> 00:25:09.950 align:middle line:84%
it is humbling as a
human computer engineer

00:25:09.950 --> 00:25:13.280 align:middle line:84%
to realize that we were told
that the extraterrestrials

00:25:13.280 --> 00:25:17.120 align:middle line:84%
responsible for these
machines and this craft

00:25:17.120 --> 00:25:23.900 align:middle line:84%
could execute with their minds
these diagrams in second.

00:25:23.900 --> 00:25:30.740 align:middle line:84%
I think that the drones are
a combination of technology

00:25:30.740 --> 00:25:33.320 align:middle line:84%
in which humans
have been involved

00:25:33.320 --> 00:25:37.090 align:middle line:84%
with the non-humans who are
the source and know about it

00:25:37.090 --> 00:25:39.890 align:middle line:84%
and that we have a
series of collaborations

00:25:39.890 --> 00:25:44.990 align:middle line:84%
between our American aerospace,
British aerospace, our allies

00:25:44.990 --> 00:25:49.650 align:middle line:84%
of World War II, literally,
with non-human intelligence who

00:25:49.650 --> 00:25:54.110 align:middle line:84%
have helped us get various
kinds of models of technology.

00:25:54.110 --> 00:25:57.650 align:middle line:84%
And somebody was experimenting
with that dragonfly drone

00:25:57.650 --> 00:25:58.910 align:middle line:90%
in 2007.

00:25:58.910 --> 00:26:00.660 align:middle line:90%
It was supposed to be invisible.

00:26:00.660 --> 00:26:02.600 align:middle line:84%
It was supposed
to stay invisible.

00:26:02.600 --> 00:26:07.000 align:middle line:84%
It was supposed to be a
monitoring device in the skies.

00:26:07.000 --> 00:26:10.160 align:middle line:84%
Somebody was jamming
the frequencies

00:26:10.160 --> 00:26:11.780 align:middle line:90%
that kept it invisible.

00:26:11.780 --> 00:26:14.330 align:middle line:84%
And that's why it would
flicker in and out.

00:26:14.330 --> 00:26:17.360 align:middle line:84%
Everybody who saw it said
it would flicker in and out.

00:26:17.360 --> 00:26:19.640 align:middle line:90%
And that gave Isaac the key.

00:26:19.640 --> 00:26:21.050 align:middle line:90%
And that's what he wrote.

00:26:21.050 --> 00:26:24.410 align:middle line:84%
I think that these
machines, why they

00:26:24.410 --> 00:26:27.470 align:middle line:84%
are being seen right now
and with the description

00:26:27.470 --> 00:26:30.290 align:middle line:84%
of flickering, that means
that there is somebody

00:26:30.290 --> 00:26:34.130 align:middle line:84%
in a military capacity who
is either experimenting with

00:26:34.130 --> 00:26:37.820 align:middle line:84%
or knows that there are
frequencies that can jam

00:26:37.820 --> 00:26:41.080 align:middle line:90%
the invisibility technology.

00:26:41.080 --> 00:26:43.580 align:middle line:84%
>> I feel that the
human-AI merger may not be

00:26:43.580 --> 00:26:46.760 align:middle line:84%
an inevitability simply
because we have learned a lot

00:26:46.760 --> 00:26:47.610 align:middle line:90%
of lessons.

00:26:47.610 --> 00:26:51.370 align:middle line:84%
And just like a baby has
to crawl before it walks,

00:26:51.370 --> 00:26:53.870 align:middle line:84%
when it starts to walk, it will
fall down a couple of times.

00:26:53.870 --> 00:26:55.578 align:middle line:84%
And we're kind of in
that phase right now

00:26:55.578 --> 00:26:58.250 align:middle line:84%
where as we get up and begin to
walk, we're going to stumble.

00:26:58.250 --> 00:27:01.100 align:middle line:84%
But every time you fall,
you remember-- the body,

00:27:01.100 --> 00:27:03.160 align:middle line:84%
the brain remembers
what caused that fall.

00:27:03.160 --> 00:27:04.760 align:middle line:90%
And it makes an adjustment.

00:27:04.760 --> 00:27:07.370 align:middle line:84%
So right now, we're
getting into AI technology.

00:27:07.370 --> 00:27:10.820 align:middle line:84%
And we're trying to utilize it
to, basically, free mankind.

00:27:10.820 --> 00:27:14.090 align:middle line:10%
Although there are some
benevolent and malevolent ways

00:27:14.090 --> 00:27:16.910 align:middle line:10%
that it can work, I do truly
believe that eventually,

00:27:16.910 --> 00:27:19.760 align:middle line:10%
in the long term, it will be
a very benevolent opportunity

00:27:19.760 --> 00:27:22.100 align:middle line:10%
for mankind to expand
itself and give

00:27:22.100 --> 00:27:25.070 align:middle line:10%
the freedom of the general
population to do work,

00:27:25.070 --> 00:27:27.140 align:middle line:10%
do the arts, do other
things that they really

00:27:27.140 --> 00:27:29.210 align:middle line:10%
would like to set
their hearts to and not

00:27:29.210 --> 00:27:31.370 align:middle line:10%
be a slave to a lot of labor.

00:27:31.370 --> 00:27:33.890 align:middle line:10%
I think it could make life
a lot easier on this planet

00:27:33.890 --> 00:27:35.535 align:middle line:10%
if it's used in the right way.

00:27:35.535 --> 00:27:37.160 align:middle line:10%
And it's a potential
that we eventually

00:27:37.160 --> 00:27:40.250 align:middle line:10%
will walk, and then also
run, and become a Type 1

00:27:40.250 --> 00:27:41.834 align:middle line:10%
and Type 2 civilization.

00:27:41.834 --> 00:27:44.500 align:middle line:90%


00:27:44.500 --> 00:27:46.790 align:middle line:84%
>> We are discovering
a larger universe.

00:27:46.790 --> 00:27:50.420 align:middle line:84%
And that same larger
universe is discovering us.

00:27:50.420 --> 00:27:54.380 align:middle line:84%
The alien presence on our planet
is the greatest mystery of all.

00:27:54.380 --> 00:27:57.380 align:middle line:84%
It forces us to ask questions
like why do they keep

00:27:57.380 --> 00:27:59.420 align:middle line:90%
their presence secret from us?

00:27:59.420 --> 00:28:03.320 align:middle line:84%
Why are they not helping
humanity in an open way?

00:28:03.320 --> 00:28:04.970 align:middle line:84%
These questions
and others will be

00:28:04.970 --> 00:28:07.850 align:middle line:84%
examined in our next
episode of "Deep Space--

00:28:07.850 --> 00:28:10.630 align:middle line:90%
Aliens and Cover-Ups."

